Pricing & Availability

Pricing for private bartending services is customized for each event. Rates vary based on event length, number of guests, and service requirements.

This approach ensures proper staffing, preparation, and a high-quality experience for every event we serve. For accurate pricing, we recommend requesting a free quote so we can tailor everything to your specific event details.

About Us

Hammerl Bar Co. was founded by a professional bartender with over three years of experience and a lifetime spent in the restaurant industry. That background created a strong focus on service, timing, and atmosphere.

Our goal is simple: deliver personalized, high-quality bar experiences that elevate private events and leave a lasting impression on guests.
